input_str: Colton Hock closed out a win for the 14th time this season -- a new school record -- and Duke Kinamon hit his second home run to lead Stanford to a 4-0 win over the University of San Francisco. Stanford (31-13) is finding ways to win a variety of ways, which you would expect from a team in the midst of winning 12 of 13 games. Two days after losing a chance to sweep Arizona State, the Cardinal remained perfect
